The paper deals with improving semantic segmentation using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of synthetic images for dataset augmentation also involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the challenges of dataset collection, which could fall under graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
